        "type": "text",
        "content": "0.K - KEYBOARD/MOUSE MAPPING SCHEMES"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Each key of the SPF/PC keyboard may be remapped to assume a new"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "function, command, data, REXX macro, or key macro.  These key"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "assignments are grouped together to form \"Keyboard Schemes,\""
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "which allow similar style key patters to be selected with a"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "single action."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "For more information on the following categories, please select"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the option by number:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1 +- Selecting Keyboard Schemes"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "2 +- Assigning values to keys"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
